disruptorC

C implementation of LMAX's disruptor pattern.

Tested on Mac OS X 10.7.4 and Fedora 17.

Build by:

      ./bootstrap 
      make

Then run the tests i test/.


TODO: 

* Use the __atomic* operations from GCC 4.7 instead of the __sync*
  functions, to fix the performance issues with __sync*.

NOTES:

* Uncomment the "CC=g++" line in configure.ac to get approximately 10%
  more performance for free.
